cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with video retrieval based on natural language queries and generating descriptions given an input video, which suggests that it could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of web image search in the sentence embedding process also suggests a potential connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the proposed embedding models and their simultaneous learning could also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG).
